---
import background from '../assets/background.svg';
---

<div id="container">
	<img id="background" src={background.src} alt="" fetchpriority="high" />
	<main>
		<section id="hero">
			<h1>Automated Coding with AI</h1>
			<p class="tagline">From GitHub issue to pull request, automatically</p>
			<p class="future-badge">The Future Is Here</p>
			<p class="hype-text">
				Experience the revolutionary power of AI-driven development. No more tedious coding. No more endless debugging sessions.
				No more context-switching between planning, implementation, and testing.
				Just describe what you need, and watch as Claude Code brings your ideas to life in seconds.
				This isn't just automation‚Äîit's a quantum leap in how software gets built.
				Imagine a world where your backlog shrinks automatically, where routine tasks complete themselves while you sleep,
				and where your team can focus on the creative challenges that truly matter.
				From bug fixes to feature implementations, from refactoring to documentation,
				every GitHub issue becomes an opportunity for autonomous execution.
				<strong>The era of autonomous development has arrived, and it's transforming how teams ship software.</strong>
			</p>
		</section>

		<section id="workflow">
			<h2>How It Works</h2>

			<p class="workflow-intro">
				Super Shepherd is an automated development workflow that transforms GitHub issues into production-ready code.
				By combining GitHub Actions with Claude Code AI, it eliminates manual coding tasks and accelerates your development cycle‚Äîsaving developers hours of routine work and delivering faster results that keep clients happy.
				Simply label an issue with <code>automated-task</code>, and watch as the entire process‚Äîfrom code generation to pull request creation‚Äîhappens automatically.
			</p>

			<div class="workflow-grid">
				<div class="workflow-step">
					<div class="step-icon">üìù</div>
					<h3>Issue Created</h3>
					<p>Create a GitHub issue with the <code>automated-task</code> label. Describe what you need built or fixed.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="workflow-arrow">‚Üì</div>

				<div class="workflow-step">
					<div class="step-icon">üîç</div>
					<h3>Bot Detects</h3>
					<p>The orchestrator polls every 30 seconds, automatically picking up new labeled issues.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="workflow-arrow">‚Üì</div>

				<div class="workflow-step">
					<div class="step-icon">ü§ñ</div>
					<h3>Claude Codes</h3>
					<p>Claude Code analyzes your repository and autonomously implements the solution.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="workflow-arrow">‚Üì</div>

				<div class="workflow-step">
					<div class="step-icon">‚úÖ</div>
					<h3>PR Created</h3>
					<p>Changes are committed, a pull request is created, and the issue is updated and closed.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</div>

<style>
	#background {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		z-index: -1;
		filter: blur(100px);
	}

	#container {
		font-family: Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Arial Nova', 'Nimbus Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
		min-height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	main {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 1200px;
		padding: 64px 32px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 80px;
	}

	#hero {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 800px;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 56px;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin: 0 0 24px 0;
		color: #111827;
		line-height: 1.1;
		background: linear-gradient(83.21deg, #3245ff 0%, #bc52ee 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	.tagline {
		font-size: 24px;
		color: #4b5563;
		margin: 0 0 32px 0;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.future-badge {
		display: inline-block;
		font-size: 18px;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
		color: #ffffff;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3245ff 0%, #bc52ee 100%);
		padding: 12px 32px;
		border-radius: 50px;
		margin: 0 0 24px 0;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(50, 69, 255, 0.3);
		animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	@keyframes pulse {
		0%, 100% {
			transform: scale(1);
			box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(50, 69, 255, 0.3);
		}
		50% {
			transform: scale(1.05);
			box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(50, 69, 255, 0.5);
		}
	}

	.hype-text {
		font-size: 20px;
		color: #374151;
		line-height: 1.8;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 16px;
	}

	.hype-text strong {
		color: #3245ff;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	#workflow {
		width: 100%;
	}

	#workflow h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 36px;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #111827;
		margin: 0 0 24px 0;
	}

	.workflow-intro {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 18px;
		color: #4b5563;
		line-height: 1.7;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 48px auto;
		padding: 0 16px;
	}

	.workflow-grid {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 24px;
	}

	.workflow-step {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
		border-radius: 16px;
		padding: 32px 24px;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 600px;
		text-align: center;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
		transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
		border: 1px solid rgba(50, 69, 255, 0.1);
	}

	.workflow-step:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 12px rgba(50, 69, 255, 0.15);
	}

	.step-icon {
		font-size: 48px;
		margin-bottom: 16px;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.workflow-step h3 {
		font-size: 20px;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #111827;
		margin: 0 0 12px 0;
	}

	.workflow-step p {
		font-size: 14px;
		color: #6b7280;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.workflow-arrow {
		font-size: 32px;
		color: #3245ff;
		font-weight: 700;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	code {
		display: inline;
		background: rgba(50, 69, 255, 0.1);
		color: #3245ff;
		border-radius: 4px;
		padding: 2px 6px;
		font-size: 13px;
		font-family: ui-monospace, 'Cascadia Code', 'Source Code Pro', Menlo, Consolas, 'DejaVu Sans Mono', monospace;
	}

	@media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
		h1 {
			font-size: 42px;
		}

		.tagline {
			font-size: 20px;
		}

		.future-badge {
			font-size: 16px;
			padding: 10px 28px;
			letter-spacing: 1.5px;
		}

		.hype-text {
			font-size: 18px;
		}

		#workflow h2 {
			font-size: 30px;
		}

		.workflow-intro {
			font-size: 16px;
		}
	}

	@media screen and (max-width: 640px) {
		main {
			padding: 48px 24px;
			gap: 60px;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 36px;
		}

		.tagline {
			font-size: 18px;
			margin-bottom: 24px;
		}

		.future-badge {
			font-size: 14px;
			padding: 8px 20px;
			letter-spacing: 1px;
		}

		.hype-text {
			font-size: 16px;
			line-height: 1.7;
		}

		#workflow h2 {
			font-size: 26px;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}

		.workflow-intro {
			font-size: 16px;
			margin-bottom: 32px;
		}

		.workflow-step {
			max-width: 400px;
		}
	}
</style>
